    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm so excited for the person who gets to take this beauty home. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
