    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to deliver 414 hp with a linear power band peaking at 8,300 RPM. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut with zero bushing play, and the EDC (Electronic Damper Control) provides instantaneous response across all drive modes. Meticulously maintained with recent preventative rod bearing service and a Blackstone oil analysis confirming internal health. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero rock chips, while the interior leather shows no bolster compression. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Garage kept. Clean title. Full service history included. No accidents or cosmetic damage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
