      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is evident from the moment you approach it. The exterior boasts a deep, showroom-quality luster with zero imperfections, protected by a recent professional ceramic coating and always stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and completely untouched by wear, smelling exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealership and a drive that is as tight and responsive as a brand-new vehicle. No stone has been left unturned in preserving this car\u2019s integrity\u2014from the spotless, dust-free engine bay to the pristine undercarriage. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a vehicle in truly peerless, investment-quality condition.",
      "price": 48900.0,
