      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept tucked away in a garage, and it is spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the full dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
